{"hash":"1b2252031807d0647a7737204bb817ac03f9fc37","data":{"post":{"id":"77","title":"换源集合","summary":"\n<p>各种换源，我要的都在这里了。针对天朝就不用国际语言了 <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"smile\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f604.png\">😄</g-emoji></p>\n","body":"\n<p>众所周知，天朝网络环境需要换源来支撑，闲言少叙：</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/</a></p>\n<h2>\n      <a id=\"article-pip\" class=\"anchor-hover\" href=\"#pip\">\n      #</a> pip</h2>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/pypi/\">https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/pypi/</a></p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-shell\"><div class=\"code-lang\">shell</div><pre><code>pip config <span class=\"pl-c1\">set</span> global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</code></pre></div>\n<h2>\n      <a id=\"article-npm\" class=\"anchor-hover\" href=\"#npm\">\n      #</a> npm</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-shell\"><div class=\"code-lang\">shell</div><pre><code>npm config <span class=\"pl-c1\">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre></div>\n<p>sharp 源</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-shell\"><div class=\"code-lang\">shell</div><pre><code>yarn config <span class=\"pl-c1\">set</span> sharp_binary_host <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/sharp<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>\n      <a id=\"article-docker\" class=\"anchor-hover\" href=\"#docker\">\n      #</a> docker</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-json\"><div class=\"code-lang\">json</div><pre><code><span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>registry-mirrors<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>: [\n  <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>https://hub-mirror.c.163.com<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>,\n]</code></pre></div>","createdAt":"2020-02-28T14:29:13.000Z","lastEditedAt":"2020-06-30T06:47:31.000Z","image":null,"labels":[{"id":"blog: cheatsheet","name":"cheatsheet","type":"blog","color":"6655d6","path":"/blog/cheatsheet/"}]}},"context":{}}